dct_title_s: MM sérkort. Ísland sérkort : Snæfellsnes sérkort 1:100 000 = Iceland, special map.
dct_description_sm: Regional topographic map with tourist features. Relief shown by contours, gradient tints, and spot heights. Depths shown by gradient tints. Panel title. "Copyright: Ólafur Valsson/Mál og menning." Includes notes. Text, distance tables, 1:500,000-scale geological map, remote-sensing map of Snæfellsjökull, 5 town tourist maps (including Stykkishólmur), and color illustrations on verso.
